{"tid":1645040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好恐佈 網上面已經有班左膠有組職咁引導人同前線割蓆 又話咩大家休息 想瓦解場運動","createTime":"2019-10-10T18:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T00:43:52.000Z","uid":252492,"like":43,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"29c9f56fdc83d3e56a3cdb2252af6265fb36f546","tid":1645040,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"打咁大篇文講到咩前線都累要放棄又話前線睇唔過眼勇武裝修<br />\n(真係手足既 你汽油彈同燒鋪都唔割蓆呀) <br />\n都係潛意識想引導睇緊既和理非同勇武割蓆<br />\n<br />\n去到最近一班打手帶風向咩唔好拆裝修<br />\n又不斷叫人休息咩都唔好做 再到鼓吹和理非進場<br />\n泛民(特別社民連) 不斷為議席派人空降 趕走其他做緊好耐地區工作既其他泛民或連登巴打<br />\n<br />\n好似成班想急住趕走勇武 由和理非主導好似雨傘咁瓦解場運動<br />\n以便佢地選舉果陣收割人血饅頭食政治利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i73OOGJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi73OOGJ.png&h=3bbac2c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdYrAmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdYrAmK.png&h=ba956f29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d7c5df885ad820cf5baff64a9e204e9ccfd918f","tid":1645040,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:04:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8dac0265c942103816bea4f5d7f057fcfda01e5","tid":1645040,"uid":84044,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"嗰啲根本仲衰撚個左膠<br />\n有冇新名詞可以形容佢"},{"pid":"c63c13c0b00886298ef4fb7b9d5de5fa917dc474","tid":1645040,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696883011266488639b79318b15b318e9ce036ed","tid":1645040,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cb9d2e3d8ea2ea4bd86c46c76f0a86c7a07608","tid":1645040,"uid":19527,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"ci